sidebar.docs.category.代币经济.link.generate.message: The total supply of $UNIT tokens is finite, but the exact limit will vary depending on the future production of rare assets. This is because Treasurenet block rewards reduce over time. Producers work together to create RWAs to prevent $UNIT block rewards from decaying quickly. Whereas BTC reduces by 50% per period, $UNIT rewards reduce at a rate based on $TAT minted, hence asset produced.
